description: Welcome home to this lovely and spacious two bedroom, two bathroom duplex residence on South Boston's red hot west side! The property lives like a small single family house with access to the wonderful back yard and deck from both levels for ease of access.  A great layout for entertaining with a good sized living space that features a gas fireplace.  This whole home underwent extensive renovations in 2017/2018 with basically everything being gutted including a new kitchen, both bathrooms, hardwood floors and all of the heating/cooling systems.  The primary suite occupies the lower level and easily accommodates a king size bed, has an incredible walk-in/dressing room set and also includes the laundry.  The deck/back yard are a true gem that provides a quiet retreat and would be great for dog lovers.  The location just a 5-7 minute walk from the Broadway Red Line stop affords incredible convenience to restaurant's, cafe's, both I-90 and I-93.  Don't miss out!
